<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Mastodon (Fediverse@Mastodon@mastodon.social)</title><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon</link><atom:link href="http://rsshub.email-once.com/fediverse/timeline/Mastodon@mastodon.social" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description>Public posts from @Mastodon@mastodon.social - Powered by RSSHub</description><generator>RSSHub</generator><webMaster>contact@rsshub.app (RSSHub)</webMaster><language>en</language><image><url>https://files.mastodon.social/accounts/avatars/000/013/179/original/b4ceb19c9c54ec7e.png</url><title>Mastodon (Fediverse@Mastodon@mastodon.social)</title><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon</link></image><lastBuildDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 21:20:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><ttl>5</ttl><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;We‚Äôll be part of the FOSDEM Social Web track on Saturday, and will be talking about the &lt;span class=&quot;h-card&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://social.ngi.eu/@ngisearch&quot; class=&quot;u-url mention&quot;&gt;@&lt;span&gt;ngisearch&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; supported Fediverse Discovery Providers &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/fediscovery&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;fediscovery&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; project: &lt;a href=&quot;https://fosdem.org/2025/schedule/event/fosdem-2025-4531-fediscovery-improving-search-and-discovery-on-the-fediverse/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;fosdem.org/2025/schedule/event&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;/fosdem-2025-4531-fediscovery-improving-search-and-discovery-on-the-fediverse/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;You‚Äôll also be able to find the team at Social Web After Hours on Sunday at HSBXL: &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.hsbxl.be/events/byteweek/2025/social-web-after-hours/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://www.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;hsbxl.be/events/byteweek/2025/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;social-web-after-hours/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113900609139086168</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113900609139086168</guid><pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 13:42:48 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;Hey friends! It‚Äôs nearly time for &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/FOSDEM&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;FOSDEM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, the annual free and open source event in Brussels. This weekend, the Mastodon team will be based in building H. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We‚Äôll be raising funds for the project with some of our merch - beautiful limited edition winter mugs, pins, and t-shirts. We‚Äôll also have fun stickers to share for free, so you can show your support for Mastodon everywhere!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;(just so you know: we‚Äôre a bit short on larger t-shirt sizes, so come early if you want to buy one of those)&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113900604787941302</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113900604787941302</guid><pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 13:41:42 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;Transparency is a key part of our transition to non-profit ownership. Follow us to stay informed about our progress, priorities, and the move to community-driven governance. Together, we&#39;re building a safer, more open Fediverse. Join us üôÇ &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.joinmastodon.org/2025/01/the-people-should-own-the-town-square/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;blog.joinmastodon.org/2025/01/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;the-people-should-own-the-town-square/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/MastodonNonProfit&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;MastodonNonProfit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113820526480156595</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113820526480156595</guid><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 10:16:44 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re not just building a social network, we&#39;re building a community. Communities thrive when everyone contributes. We&#39;re growing our operating budget to invest in our contribution to the Fediverse as a whole, including our commitment to trust and safety, and user experience. Donate to support this vision! &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://joinmastodon.org/sponsors#donate&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;joinmastodon.org/sponsors#dona&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;te&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/MastodonNonProfit&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;MastodonNonProfit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113820524715268095</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113820524715268095</guid><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 10:16:17 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;Our core mission remains the same: create tools and spaces for authentic online communities. No changes to your user experience, just a stronger commitment to transparency and community-driven governance. Join us on this journey!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/MastodonNonProfit&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;MastodonNonProfit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113820523713523115</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113820523713523115</guid><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 10:16:02 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;Eugen&#39;s vision for Mastodon was centered on user choice, community, and freedom. Now, we&#39;re formalizing that commitment with the formation of a new European non-profit entity. Eugen will transition to an alternative role in the team, with a new CEO to be announced very soon. Stay tuned for updates on these changes. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/MastodonNonProfit&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;MastodonNonProfit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113820522826128588</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113820522826128588</guid><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 10:15:48 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;Today Mastodon is taking another step towards its founding ideals: independence and non-profit ownership. We&#39;re transferring ownership of key assets to a new, European not-for-profit entity, ensuring our mission remains true to a decentralised social web, not corporate control. &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/MastodonNonProfit&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;MastodonNonProfit&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.joinmastodon.org/2025/01/the-people-should-own-the-town-square/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;blog.joinmastodon.org/2025/01/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;the-people-should-own-the-town-square/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113820521450833408</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113820521450833408</guid><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 10:15:27 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;Not sure what you&#39;re getting? Someone made a video review of the toy, so you can see it in action. You can also browse the &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Plushtodon&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Plushtodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; hashtag to see the elephants on their adventures.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=69fgnoyBczs&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://www.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;youtube.com/watch?v=69fgnoyBczs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113761158787080236</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113761158787080236</guid><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 22:38:45 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;Only about half of &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Mastodon&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Mastodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; stuffed toys are still in stock in the US. Help us pay our bills *and* get a friend-shaped travel and business companion! &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Plushtodon&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Plushtodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://shop.joinmastodon.org/products/mastodon-plushie&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;shop.joinmastodon.org/products&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;/mastodon-plushie&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113761144491567042</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113761144491567042</guid><pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 22:35:07 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;If you&#39;re curious how &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Mastodon&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Mastodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is doing by the numbers, the 2023 Annual Report is finally here. How large is our budget, and where does it go? Who works on Mastodon? For all of this and more, we&#39;ve got an answer--at least as far as 2023 goes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.joinmastodon.org/2024/12/annual-report-2023/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;blog.joinmastodon.org/2024/12/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;annual-report-2023/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113703731057376701</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113703731057376701</guid><pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 19:14:07 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Mastodon&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Mastodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; stuffed toy is now available in the United States! This is a limited run of 500. Check out the &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Plushtodon&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Plushtodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; hashtag for more pictures!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://shop.joinmastodon.org/products/mastodon-plushie&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;shop.joinmastodon.org/products&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;/mastodon-plushie&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113675185147002558</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113675185147002558</guid><pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 18:14:31 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;Thank you, Mastodon community! üéâ &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Thanks to your incredible support, this Giving Tuesday we‚Äôve raised $10,438 (13% of $75,000 goal) for our ‚ú® Trust &amp;amp; Safety Lead ‚ú®&amp;nbsp;hire!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;There‚Äôs still time ‚è≥&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Every contribution brings us closer to building a safer, more inclusive, open &amp;amp; free community-led platform where people, not profit, shape the future.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Thank you for donating, spreading the word &amp;amp; being part of this journey! üíô&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Help us reach our campaign goal: &lt;a href=&quot;https://givebutter.com/givingmastodon&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;givebutter.com/givingmastodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/GivingTuesday&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;GivingTuesday&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113631034747345380</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113631034747345380</guid><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 23:06:30 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;Our &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/GivingTuesday&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;GivingTuesday&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; campaign is officially LIVE!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We‚Äôre raising $75,000 to fund a new hire: ‚ú® Trust &amp;amp; Safety Lead ‚ú®&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;A crucial role in protecting Mastodon‚Äôs growing community by strengthening our trust &amp;amp; safety tools incl. &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/moderation&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;moderation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; server blocklists.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Your support is an investment in the future of a decentralised, free and respectful online community, where every user feels safe &amp;amp; supported.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Thank you for being part of this movement! üí™&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Donate what you can today: &lt;a href=&quot;https://givebutter.com/givingmastodon&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;givebutter.com/givingmastodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113590455940377224</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113590455940377224</guid><pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 19:06:46 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;We believe the internet should be a place where everyone feels safe, respected and empowered to connect.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;That‚Äôs why this &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/GivingTuesday&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;GivingTuesday&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; we‚Äôre launching a campaign to fund a vital new role at &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Mastodon&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Mastodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;‚ú® Trust &amp;amp; Safety Lead ‚ú®&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;With the recent US elections and many changes to come, protecting our community has never been more important.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We officially kick off on *Tue, Dec 3rd* but if you‚Äôd like, you can make an impact today. Thank you for your support!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://givebutter.com/givingmastodon&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;givebutter.com/givingmastodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113585117333350948</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113585117333350948</guid><pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 20:29:06 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;Finally, the &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Plushtodon&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Plushtodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is available for purchase in the UK! Only 90 left in all of Europe! We&#39;re still working on unlocking selling to the US üôÇ &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://shop.joinmastodon.org/products/mastodon-plushie&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;shop.joinmastodon.org/products&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;/mastodon-plushie&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113550082153603024</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113550082153603024</guid><pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 15:59:11 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re now shipping the &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Plushtodon&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Plushtodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to Norway and Switzerland! Only 173 left in Europe. News on the US and other regions to come soon!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://shop.joinmastodon.org/products/mastodon-plushie&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;shop.joinmastodon.org/products&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;/mastodon-plushie&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113344435853077322</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113344435853077322</guid><pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 08:20:38 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;* We&#39;re waiting for our UK VAT number before enabling shipping to the UK to avoid you having to pay any unexpected duties on the package. As for the US, the stock hasn&#39;t arrived at the warehouse yet.&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113312118225192574</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113312118225192574</guid><pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 15:21:50 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;The wait is over*‚ÄîThe &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Mastodon&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Mastodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; stuffed toy is now available for purchase in the EU! Other regions to come later. Share your pictures with the &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Plushtodon&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Plushtodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; hashtag!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://shop.joinmastodon.org/products/mastodon-plushie&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;shop.joinmastodon.org/products&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;/mastodon-plushie&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113312100548054021</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113312100548054021</guid><pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 15:17:20 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Mastodon&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Mastodon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 4.3 is out! üéâ We&#39;ve made notifications easier to manage and improved the look and feel of the whole app across the board. And that&#39;s just the tip of the iceberg! See what you can expect once your server upgrades:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.joinmastodon.org/2024/10/mastodon-4.3/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;blog.joinmastodon.org/2024/10/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;mastodon-4.3/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113272025176822566</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/113272025176822566</guid><pubDate>Tue, 08 Oct 2024 13:25:38 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title></title><description>&lt;p&gt;We‚Äôre hiring again! The Mastodon team is looking for a part-time &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Finance&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Finance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; / &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Ops&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Ops&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Associate to support &lt;span class=&quot;h-card&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/@mellifluousbox&quot; class=&quot;u-url mention&quot;&gt;@&lt;span&gt;mellifluousbox&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; + &lt;span class=&quot;h-card&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/@Gargron&quot; class=&quot;u-url mention&quot;&gt;@&lt;span&gt;Gargron&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This is a &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/remote&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;remote&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; position and requires working proficiency in &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/German&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;German&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Ideally:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;‚Ä∫ You have experience in &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/accounting&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;accounting&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; + &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/bookkeeping&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;bookkeeping&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;‚Ä∫ Understand German &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/legal&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;legal&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; frameworks + systems&lt;br&gt;‚Ä∫ Are great with MS &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/Excel&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;Excel&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Could also work as a long-term paid &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/internship&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;internship&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Can you refer anyone to us? More info/to apply:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jobs.ashbyhq.com/mastodon/f38df483-da29-4bab-9f0c-5d1b11e7c1d0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;jobs.ashbyhq.com/mastodon/f38d&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;f483-da29-4bab-9f0c-5d1b11e7c1d0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/FediHire&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;FediHire&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/GetFediHired&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;GetFediHired&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://mastodon.social/tags/hiring&quot; class=&quot;mention hashtag&quot; rel=&quot;tag&quot;&gt;#&lt;span&gt;hiring&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><link>https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/112769333503182077</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://mastodon.social/@Mastodon/112769333503182077</guid><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 18:44:32 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>